WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.800
Stop babysitting AI coding work.
AI coding does not lack models.
It lacks a command tower.

00:03.800 --> 00:07.800
One operator loop, not five scattered tools.
OpenVibeCoding turns PM intake,
Command Tower, Workflow Cases, and Proof & Replay
into one governed operating path.

00:07.800 --> 00:11.000
Read the board before you trust the result.
Track live work, queue posture, blocker risk,
and proof readiness before promotion or replay.

00:11.000 --> 00:14.000
The same command tower lives on desktop, too.
The desktop shell keeps PM loop, hotkeys,
drawers, and proof surfaces aligned with the web operator surface.

00:14.000 --> 00:18.000
Repo-backed. Proof-first. Read-only MCP.
Start with one proven workflow.
Then choose the adoption path that matches the real job.
